# Vercel v2 (IMA camp) — no automatic summer camp deploy

**Do not** run a production deploy to **`ima-summer-camp`** (`ima-summer-camp.vercel.app`) after edits in this repo unless the user **explicitly** asks to deploy (e.g. “deploy”, “ship to prod”, “vercel prod”).

- Rely on git-push auto deploy or the user’s own workflow unless they request a CLI deploy.
- If they do ask for a forced production deploy to summer camp, from repo root:

```bash
cd /Users/tomrichardson/Downloads/vercel-v2 && VERCEL_ORG_ID=team_PXMrLfQ01zlse3XBsDcaPa3s VERCEL_PROJECT_ID=prj_TJxRFRbKAK4AkYBe8AKL1DoH2k9p npx vercel deploy --prod --yes
```

- Optional: `npx vercel --prod --yes` from this folder targets the linked project (`vercel-v2-alpha.vercel.app`), not summer camp, unless configured otherwise.
